name: Pareidolia
description:
Pareidolia is part of the Cajal series that takes inspiration from Santiago Ramon Cajal’s illustrations of neurones. These artworks have been crafted with thoughtful insight and tender loving care. On a technical level, they mix home-brewed generative systems with hand-drawn images using Processing and GANs. 

In celebration of #HEN500K

Size : 3318x4698px PNG [bitmap image]
